Energy Resistance +1; Feather Falling; Invisibility; Jumping; Meld Into Stone; Mind Shielding; Protection (up to +2); Spell Storing, Minor; Sustenance; Swimming

</div>

</div>

</div></font><br />
<br />
<font face="Arial">    * Armor &amp; Shield (in addition to, and must have at least, an enhancement bonus of +1): <div style="margin:5px 20px 20px 20px">

